const content = `If you have ever wondered why some people consistently make better decisions, build more successful businesses, and navigate life with unusual clarity — the answer often comes down to the mental models they use. Mental models are frameworks for thinking. They are cognitive tools that help you understand complex situations, avoid common mistakes, and see patterns that others miss. The world's most successful people — from Warren Buffett to Charlie Munger, from Elon Musk to Naval Ravikant — have spoken openly about how mental models shaped their thinking and their outcomes. In this guide, you will discover the 15 most powerful mental models that high achievers use every day — and how you can start applying them immediately.`;
